      <scopecontent id="aspace_9bb0ad9009cdb178612c12ce20f39484">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>A collection of twenty-five posters documenting Yiddish theater in Argentina and Poland during the years 1917-1958. Most posters feature the work of Yiddish poet, writer, editor and playwright Nechemia Zucker. The collection also contains a folder of newspaper clippings, advertisements, title pages, journals, and works written or edited by Nechemia Zucker.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
